EN: The chairman demanded that all members adhere to the rules of the meeting.

ZH: 主席在困难时刻展现出了领导者的风范。
EN: The chairman showed leadership in difficult times.

ZH: 主席亲自检查了项目的进展情况。
EN: The chairman personally inspected the progress of the project.

